[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]The above
[normal] statistics demonstrate that the BBC is a giant media entity in television,
[normal] 
[normal]radio and online and that it is a dominant presence on each of these platforms.
[normal] 
[normal]Furthermore it must not be forgotten that in the present day the dominance in these
[normal] 
[normal]major three plat
[normal]forms has an interactive effect such as to 
[normal]supercharg[bold]e the overall
[normal] 
[normal]impact of the BBC.
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]It is also important to note that for all of its claims to special status (stemming from a
[normal] 
[normal]Royal Charter, Editorial Guidelines, etc. etc.), in the all-important TV and o
[normal]nline
[normal] 
[normal]platforms the BBC is not awarded by the British public with a unique and lofty status
[normal] 
[normal]for impartiality or trustworthiness.
